    <updated>2018-01-06T15:31:44.460Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##前言</p><ul><li><p>Markown是一种轻量级的<strong>[标记语言]</strong>，语法简单，一劳永逸。</p></li><li><p>“面向内容”，没有花哨的格式、排版和字体设置，可以导出HTML、PDF和本身的.md文件。</p></li><li><p>现在越来越多的写作爱好者开始使用它，特别是程序员。</p></li></ul><a id="more"></a><ul><li><p>假如需要做有含有许多图表、图片，或者流程图、时序图等特殊文档时，更好的方式是使用其他专用软件，这样会更省时省力。</p></li><li><p>使用Markdown本身就是一件简单、纯粹的时间，切勿本末倒置。</p></li></ul><p>##简要规则</p><ul><li><h3 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h3></li></ul><p>用<code>#</code>的数量来定义文字大小，越多字体越小，最多六个</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>一级标题  ```   </span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">``` ## 二级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>三级标题 ```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 无序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 示范</span><br><span class="line">* 示范</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 有序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1. 示范</span><br><span class="line">2. 示范</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 引用 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; 标准的markdown语法需要在符号后面加一个空格</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 图片和链接</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[] 中括号里写链接的文字说明，圆括号里写链接地址</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[百度](http://www.baidu.com)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">添加图片与添加链接十分相似，只是前面多了一个感叹号(注意是英文符号)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![非常喜欢的图片](http://p22ih0wv4.bkt.clouddn.com/999.jpg &quot;上一个网站的背景图&quot; )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 更改图片大小</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">markdown兼容HTML语法，利用`&lt;img&gt;`标签来定义图片大小</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">长宽可以用数值如300</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="filename" width="300""" heigth="300"""><br></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">也可以用比例</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="filename" width="50%""" heigth="50%"""><br></p><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`=` 号前面有一个空格</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">如果想要图片居中，只要在外面保卫div标签就可以了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="filename" width="300""" heigth="300"""><br></p><div align="center"><br></div><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 粗体和斜体</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">粗体用左右两个星号包含，斜体用左右一个星号包含</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**粗体** *斜体*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* ### 表格</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">各字段用`|`分开，在回车键上方。第一属性行与下面各行要用`:-:|:-:|:-:|`来分隔开，其中`:`为可选，出现`-`两边，表示文本靠左或者靠右，左右都写就居中，一个都不写就默认靠右</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">name|id|birth</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">:-|:-:|-:</span></span><br><span class="line">leonleon|               777777777    |fdfsdfsd1996</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">leon|fff|jjjj</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute"></span></span><br><span class="line">* ### 代码块</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">单行代码 ``` ` ```在tab键上方，不是单引号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">` this is code ` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">多行代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>this is code</code></pre><p>```</p><p>使用Windows平台的MarkdownPad2编辑器的时候，代码块内有换行和符号转义的问题，需要在窗口上方<code>工具</code>-<code>选项</code>中Markdown选项卡中的Markdown处理器选择为<code>Github风格Markdown（离线）</code></p><ul><li><h3 id="字符转义"><a href="#字符转义" class="headerlink" title="字符转义"></a>字符转义</h3></li></ul><p>更大多数编程语言中类似，在字符前面加反斜线 <code>\</code></p><ul><li><h3 id="文章折叠"><a href="#文章折叠" class="headerlink" title="文章折叠"></a>文章折叠</h3></li></ul><p>在文章需要开始折叠的地方加入下面的代码<code>&lt;!--more--&gt;</code>，就会在文章静态网页里的相应地方显示<code>&gt;&gt;more</code>字样。建议在文章第一段后加入。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;##前言&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Markown是一种轻量级的&lt;strong&gt;[标记语言]&lt;/strong&gt;，语法简单，一劳永逸。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;“面向内容”，没有花哨的格式、排版和字体设置，可以导出HTML、PDF和本身的.md文件。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;现在越来越多的写作爱好者开始使用它，特别是程序员。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
